{"title":"满江红四首","authors":["郭沫若"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"满江红四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向解放军学习"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命功臣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁当数"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凌烟第一？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无疑问，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武装部队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咸推巨擘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上三山凭荡扫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间百垢教湔滌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是阿谁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲手铸成之？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标原则；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八个字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"具威力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好作风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奠定了新中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士人人争五好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寰球处处称无敌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都向解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤学习！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下乡去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下农村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由来是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家基础。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃穿用，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民所赖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕植为主。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海山林余虎豹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年城社藏狐鼠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"廓清之，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷厉以风行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无容恕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫农组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下中户；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擎天柱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成核心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严整斗争队伍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灭资兴无施教育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防修反特凭部署。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争做接班人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下乡去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比学赶帮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见贤思齐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图强发奋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"况工业"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"位居主导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂容迟顿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝胆卧薪甘似蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程门立雪道唯问！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争上游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精以更求精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳而很！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮后进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用千方百计"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进攻头阵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"努力追求现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾心卷起风雷迅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正当仁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不让于师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地天震。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂石油自给"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴煤油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一珠血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人都知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因循苟且，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩头乞讨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命运全凭天摆布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咽喉一任人掐倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉门关，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锁钥也因人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堪愤恼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破迷信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碎镣铐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主奖励，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅三年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地底潜龙飞跃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众志成城四第一，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁人如海全五好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂今朝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放地球军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强哉矫！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}